---
title: Saucy Sweet Chilli Pork & Udon Noodles with Crispy Shallots
description: This saucy noodle number puts a hearty, soupy twist on a pork stir-fry. Moreish pork mince and veggies are coated in a mouth-watering sweet chilli and coconut sauce, then topped with a sprinkling of crispy shallots for extra crunch.

*Unfortunately, this week's coriander was in short supply, so we've replaced it with spring onion. Don't worry, the recipe will be just as delicious!*
